{
  "texts": [
    "Implicit communication, collaboration, and memory are key.",
    "B.1 Game DescriptionWe structure the game description of Hanabi into the overall objective, and the rules of the game.The card game Hanabi has the following rules:-The game uses a 50-card deck, divided into five colours (red (R), green (G), blue (B), yellow (Y), white (W)).",
    "Each color has cards of ranks 1 to 5.",
    "Each color has with three 1's, two 2's, two 3's, two 4's, one 5.-Players have to create stacks of each color.",
    "Each color stack starts with a Rank 1 card and goes up one by one in ascending order up to Rank 5."
  ]
}